#: ../../docs/training_manual/forestry/index.rst:3
msgid "Module: Forestry Application"
msgstr "Modul: Primena u šumarstvu"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/forestry/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"In modules 1 through 13, you have already learned quite a lot about QGIS and"
" how to work with it. If you are interested in learning about some basic "
"forestry applications of GIS, following this module will give you the "
"ability to apply what you have learned and will show you some new useful "
"tools."
msgstr ""
"U modulima od 1 do 13, već ste dosta naučili o QGIS-u i kako da radite sa "
"njim. Ako ste zainteresovani da saznate više o nekim osnovnim primenama "
"GIS-a u šumarstvu, praćenje ovog modula će vam dati mogućnost da "
"primenite ono što ste naučili i pokazaće vam neke nove korisne alate."

